Alex Impey, a father-of-two, is selling marijuana to those suffering from serious illness .
His hemp store, Gnostic Hemporium, north of Sydney, has 20 requests for help each week at his hemp store .
Some cancer sufferers can use up to a gram each day as treatment with costs between $80 and $150 per gram .
The medicinal marijuana is as simple as placing into food or bottles for babies .